               <div class="module l-12 fix vspace-xs">
                  	
                  <h1 class="size-5">
                     		We’re very sorry – we can’t sign you up
                     	
                  </h1>
                  	
                  	
                  
               </div>
            </div>
         </div>
         <div class="container l-12 center vspace-s vspace-top-0">
            <div class="container l-12 fix">
               <div id="oneandonecontent" class="module l-12 fix vspace-s oneandonecontent">
                  	
                  <!--Suspend Topictitle in normal mode-->
                  <!--1-->
                  	
                  	
                  		
                  <div class="p">
                     			
                     <div>
                        <section class="note message info"><span class="m info info vspace-bottom-0 icon"></span><strong>Important Information:</strong> 
                           <p>Your IP address suggests you are trying to sign up in a country where GMX
                              				registration is no longer possible. Unfortunately, this means we can’t create an account for you.  
                           </p>
                        </section>
                     </div> 
                     		
                  </div>
                  		
                  <p class="p">If you are sure to be seated in an allowed country but use a mobile device with a different language setting rather than "en-us"
                     or "en-uk" (f.e. for Germany "de-de"). Please try to use one of these settings for that country you want to register to.
                  </p>
                  		
                  <p class="p">
                     			We appreciate your interest in our email service. If you are located in Germany,
                     			Austria, or Switzerland, why not sign up with GMX in your country ? 
                     		
                  </p>
                  		
                  <p class="p">
                     			Germany:<a class="external" href="https://registrierung.gmx.net" target="_blank">GMX.NET</a>
                     		
                  </p>
                  		
                  <p class="p">
                     			Austria:<a class="external" href="https://registrierung.gmx.net/?defaultCountry=AT" target="_blank">GMX.AT</a>
                     		
                  </p>
                  		
                  <p class="p">
                     			Switzerland:<a class="external" href="https://registrierung.gmx.net/?defaultCountry=CH" target="_blank">GMX.CH</a>
                     		
                  </p>
                  	
                  
               </div>
            </div>
         </div>
